        <td data-label="PWA">Same as your website</td>
        <td data-label="Cross-Platform">Integrate to SFCC via OCAPI/Shop API or headless layer</td>
        <td data-label="Headless">Expose commerce via APIs; mobile consumes the headless layer</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th scope="row">Maintenance</th>
        <td class="mob" data-label="MobiLoud">One codebase; MobiLoud handles app updates</td>
        <td data-label="PWA">One web codebase</td>
        <td data-label="Cross-Platform">Separate mobile codebase + web to maintain</td>
